name: Women's 'Eternity' Boots (Yellow)
description:
Designer: Sennda of Emrayur

With every stunning outfit there is a pair of boots to tie the look together. Each piece is handcrafted from the softest genetically enhanced livestock leather, dyed a luxurious yellow with black detailing, and embedded with specialized nanofibers to give it a unique brilliant finish. Paired with the 'Eternity' suit and top, these striking boots are the culmination of a look designed to turn heads.
